Products.description: The Trae Young 2018-19 Panini Prizm Rookie is his most iconic base rookie card. As part of a remarkable 2018 NBA rookie class along with Luka Doncic, DeAndre Ayton, and Shai Gilgeous-Alexander, Trae is an exciting part of the NBA's future. Channeling Stephen Curry, Trae's game and playing style, centered on the three point shot, fits in seamlessly within the modern NBA. After a phenomenal second season where he scored and passed the ball at an extremely high level, Trae is an elite offensive player on a fast track to becoming one of the best point guards in recent memory. His Prizm rookie card is a great card to own going forward.
